{"tid":2271863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"為搵錢狂諗計｜TVB推經典角色系列 一套廿個「LEGO人仔」5個係差人","createTime":"2020-11-04T19:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T04:52:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfbd6424f79d37299bb14be51afeecc688df200","tid":2271863,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T19:16:17.000Z","msg":"因為被指新聞立場偏頗，近年TVB不但被網民封為「CCTVB」，更發起罷買在TVB落廣告的產品或服務，令TVB近年廣告數目大幅下滑。為諗計增加收入，TVB不時推出「自家精品」，多年前自創酷似「吉祥物」的TVBuddy之後，大量推出相關產品，例如鎖匙扣、水杯等，去年TVB更推出「港姐后冠套裝」，並打入淘寶，幫內地觀眾實現「港姐夢」。<br />\n<br />\n日前TVB又有新產品，推出「經典劇集角色模型系列」，以「Lego人仔」扮成不同TVB經典角色造型，例如《上海灘》的許文強（周潤發飾）、《萬水千山總是情》的莊夢蝶（汪明荃飾）等，全套20個「Lego人」，當中有5個是警察角色，包括《獵鷹》、《新紮師兄》、《刑事偵輯檔案》、《陀槍師姐》及《鐵馬戰車》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_765255_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_765255_0&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=8531187f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_765255_0&h=3143eab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_765255_0</a>"},{"pid":"6d322825409f2fdb4abff84200259e02d3f3d085","tid":2271863,"uid":1130,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T19:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/05/032300_217ae9643ef075abbf2c16eceb1acfd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F05%2F032300_217ae9643ef075abbf2c16eceb1acfd3.jpg&h=b64c5be5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc8d97d597f3bcdc8a7e700f66b4feb93f5d2c3b","tid":2271863,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}